0.1
	- Initial release

0.2
	- Title and background auto-hide after 5 seconds
	- Title and settings appear when the widget is moved or the app activated
	- It is now possible to set the orientation of the board
	- Add button to change the board orientation ingame
	- Fixed 32bit support (was providing the wrong pyd file)
	- Cleaned up boards inner border and opacity
	- Add option for custom board if a file with name board_<username>.png
	  exists

0.3
	- Add support for timed raced (Thanks to Ch4rL1E on AC forums for the patch!)
	- Add option to only display surnames
	- Hide pitboard in replay mode
	- Fix rounding "display error" in some corner cases
